---
// Garage section - Teaser for personal projects page
---

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-mono font-semibold">The Garage</h2>
    <a href="/garage" class="text-sm font-mono text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">
      See all →
    </a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="card p-6 md:p-8">
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
      Where the side projects live — the stuff I build because I can't <em>not</em> build it.
    </p>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-6">
      Once a mechanic, always a mechanic. The tools just got more abstract.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="https://openengram.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-4 rounded border border-[var(--color-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <p class="font-mono font-semibold">Engram</p>
          <span class="tag">Live</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-2">Memory infrastructure for AI agents. Self-hosted or cloud.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)]">
          <span>4,500+ memories</span>
          <span>1,500+ tests</span>
          <span>Apache 2.0</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/garage" class="block p-4 rounded border border-[var(--color-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
          <p class="font-mono font-semibold">UltraEdge</p>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-muted)]">Beta</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Endurance event planning app. React Native + Supabase.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
